rows.name:
Harghal returned to her
parents' home in Alba Margen
in the Superbian Empire.

rows.label: qst200206_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't know the location of the house,
but she said it wasn't a rich family, so
I suppose it is that kind of place.

rows.label: qst200206_msg0003
rows.name:
If you happen to meet Harghal,
pass on word about me, okay?

rows.label: qst200206_msg0105
rows.name:
She was Bahn's favorite, good at
dancing, and pampered by everyone[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200206_msg0106
rows.name:
In the end, she betrayed me and
disappeared! I don't know anything
about a girl like that!
